Recognizing the growing importance of information and the need to protect it, Bauchman and his team have made a number of strategic acquisitions to expand the company's ability to help consumers and businesses secure and manage their growing dependence on online, real-time information. With global operations in more than 40 countries, the company is viewed as a strategic partner to its customers, providing a broad range of security, storage, availability, and performance management solutions to help them proactively manage their IT infrastructure.